int64_t *  symbolPtr 
)
inlinestatic

Static inlined function DPU_DopplerProcDSP_compensateSingleValue.

Description : Compensation of Doppler phase shift in one symbol. The phase shift read from the table using half of the object Doppler index value. If the Doppler index is odd, an extra half of the bin phase shift is added. Compensation coefficient(16I|16Q) is multiplied to all symbols.
Parameters
[in]dopplerIdx: Doppler index of the object
[in]numDopplerBins: Number of Doppler bins
[in]dftSinCosTable: Table with cos/sin values exp(1j*2*pi*k/N) SIN in even position, COS in odd position, (ImRe format) for k=0,...,N-1 where N is number of Doppler bins.
[in]dftHalfBin: exp(1j*2*pi* 0.5 /N), ImRe format.
[in,out]symbolPtr: Pointer to symbol to be Doppler compensated (32Q|32I each) must be 64 bit aligned. ReIm format.
Returns
void

uint32_t *  dftHalfBin,
uint32_t *  coeff 
)
inlinestatic

DPU_DopplerProcDSP_compensationGetCoeff.

Description : Get compensation coefficient for Doppler compensation, by reading the phase shift from the table using half of the object Doppler index value. If the Doppler index is odd, an extra half of the bin phase shift is added.
Parameters
[in]dopplerIdx: Doppler index of the object
[in]numDopplerBins: Number of Doppler bins
[in]dftSinCosTable: Table with cos/sin values exp(1j*2*pi*k/N) SIN in even position, COS in odd position, for k=0,...,N-1 where N is number of Doppler bins.
[in]dftHalfBin: exp(1j*2*pi* 0.5 /N) (ImRe format)
[out]coeff: Pointer to store the compensation coefficient(ImRe format)
Returns
void

DPU_DopplerProcDSP_mult16x32cplx.

Description : Multiply a 16-bit complex to a 32-bit complex symbol.
Parameters
[in]xIQ: 16-bit complex value(16I|16Q packed in 32bits). ImRe format.
[in]wQI: 32-bit complex value(32Q|32I packed in 64bits). ReIm format.
[out]yQI: pointer to store output 32-bit complex value(32Q|32I). ReIm format.
Returns
void
